# Environment Variables for HuggingFace Spaces

# LTX-2 Model Checkpoint
# Type: Secret (path)
# Download from: https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-2.3/blob/main/ltx-2.3-22b-dev.safetensors
LTX2_CHECKPOINT_PATH=/mnt/data/ltx-2.3-22b-dev.safetensors

# Distilled LoRA for Stage 2 Refinement
# Type: Secret (path)
# Download from: https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-2.3/blob/main/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-lora-384-1.1.safetensors
LTX2_DISTILLED_LORA_PATH=/mnt/data/ltx-2.3-22b-distilled-lora-384-1.1.safetensors

# Spatial Upsampler for 2x Resolution Increase
# Type: Secret (path)
# Download from: https://huggingface.co/Lightricks/LTX-2.3/blob/main/ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors
LTX2_SPATIAL_UPSAMPLER_PATH=/mnt/data/ltx-2.3-spatial-upscaler-x2-1.1.safetensors

# Gemma 3 Text Encoder Directory
# Type: Secret (path)
# Download all files from: https://huggingface.co/google/gemma-3-12b-it-qat-q4_0-unquantized/tree/main
LTX2_GEMMA_ROOT=/mnt/data/gemma-3-12b-it-qat-q4_0-unquantized

# Instructions for HuggingFace Spaces:
# 1. Go to Settings → Variables and secrets
# 2. Click "Add secret" for EACH variable (secrets are hidden from git)
# 3. Copy the key and value from this file
# 4. Click Save
#
# Important: Use "Add secret" not "Add variable" so paths don't appear in git history!
